clean_text:
Preparation of the Starfish-Shaped Co3O4/ZnFe2O4 Hollow Nanocomposites

The starfish-shaped Co3O4/ZnFe2O4 hollow nanocomposites were obtained by a simple heating process of the as-synthesized Co3O4/FeIII-MOF-5 in the tube furnace in air at 500 °C for 2 h with a heating rate of 1 °C min-1.
